quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  45,1,"Haa, Miim"
  45,2,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, Fooluɗo, Ñeeño On"
  45,3,"Pellet, hino e tagugol kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin, maandeeji wonannde gomɗimɓe ɓen"
  45,4,"Hino e tagugol on ngol kadi, e kon ko O saaki e ruugayɗi, ko maandeeji wonannde yimɓe yananaaɓe ɓen"
  45,5,"E luutondirgol jemma e ñalorma ngol, e kon ko Allah jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e toɓo, O wuurnitiri ngo leydi ndin ɓaawo ndi yoorude, e firlitagol keneeli ɗin, ko maandeeji wonannde yimɓe haqqilooɓe ɓen"
  45,6,"Ɗin ko maandeeji Allah ɗi Men janngirante hoore goonga. E ko honɗum e yewtere ɓe gomɗinta, ɓaawo [yewtere] Allah nden e Aayeeje Makko ɗen"
  45,7,Bone woodanii kala fenoowo bakkondinɗo
  45,8,"Mo no nana Aayeeje Allah ɗen hino janngee e dow makko, refti o hedditora e townitaare, wa si tawii o nanaali ɗe. Awa wewlinir mo lepte muusuɗe"
  45,9,"Si o anndii goɗɗum e Aayeeje Amen ɗen, o jogitora ɗum jalnori. Ɓen ɗon, hino woodani lepte hoynooje"
  45,10,"Jahannama hino caggal maɓɓe. Ko ɓe faggitinoo duncanoytaaɓe hay huunde, wanaa kon ko ɓe jogitinoo yiɗɓe ko wonaa Allah. Hino woodani ɓe lepte mawɗe"
  45,11,"Ndee [Deftere]ko peewal. Ɓen yedduɓe non Aayeeje Joomi maɓɓe ɗen, hino woodani lepte soɓuɗe muusuɗe"
  45,12,"Ko Alla oon woni ko eeltanta mon maaya ngam laaɗe ndoga e hengo e dow yamiroore Makko, ngam ɗaɓɓon e ɓural Makko e yaama joo njetton"
  45,13,"O eeltani on ko woni e kammuuji e ka leydi fof, wonii e ɗuum kaawisaaji wonande yimɓe miijatooɓe"